race.description: Tabtouch - Have You Got The Touch Maiden
race.comment: LOVIN' ON ME (8) has switched to the Paul Hunter barn since her last start 74 days ago, beaten 2.3L at Bunbury most recently. The form out of that race has been sound and she has the speed to roll across from barrier 10. Comes here on the fresh side again and can salute in this easier assignment. CRASHED AND BURNED (5) just missed here fresh before the saddle shifted last time out and he finished 4.8L off the winner. Faithfull now replaces the apprentice hoop third-up into the campaign. Looked a nice horse on the rise at his first-up effort and a return to that form would see him go close. MISS FINKMEYER (11) trialled well at Lark Hill recently and can turn in a bold performance fresh. The draw is sticky, but with some luck she can make her presence felt. REGGIO CALABRIA (1) wasn't far away last week and has claims. GROMMET (7) can be in the finish on debut.
